1
00:00:06,048 --> 00:00:08,609
(1993, a year before
establishing Deep In The Bustle)

2
00:00:20,864 --> 00:00:21,743
Feng,

3
00:00:22,424 --> 00:00:23,464
why are you so late?

4
00:00:24,104 --> 00:00:24,663
Sit.

5
00:00:24,744 --> 00:00:26,023
Lu is already drunk.

6
00:00:27,863 --> 00:00:28,543
Jiasheng,

7
00:00:29,063 --> 00:00:29,584
let us

8
00:00:29,584 --> 00:00:31,023
toast

9
00:00:31,144 --> 00:00:32,063
Wei and Manni.

10
00:00:32,584 --> 00:00:33,663
Otherwise, we three

11
00:00:33,663 --> 00:00:35,663
can't even find a place to drink.

12
00:00:35,663 --> 00:00:36,163
Don't.

13
00:00:36,363 --> 00:00:36,863
Come on.

14
00:00:36,863 --> 00:00:37,703
Drink up.

15
00:00:37,703 --> 00:00:38,624
- Come on.
- Come on.

16
00:00:38,624 --> 00:00:39,584
Thanks.

17
00:00:39,743 --> 00:00:40,304
Feng,

18
00:00:40,343 --> 00:00:42,143
you're talking like a stranger now.

19
00:00:43,743 --> 00:00:44,343
Back then

20
00:00:44,343 --> 00:00:47,304
I started following you at 15.

21
00:00:47,703 --> 00:00:48,824
If it weren't for you,

22
00:00:49,463 --> 00:00:50,184
I wouldn't know

23
00:00:50,184 --> 00:00:51,703
if I'd have lived to this day.

24
00:00:51,944 --> 00:00:53,023
Honestly, Feng,

25
00:00:54,063 --> 00:00:55,864
working for you

26
00:00:56,743 --> 00:00:57,904
is a blessing for me.

27
00:00:57,904 --> 00:00:58,743
Feng, a toast to you.

28
00:00:59,143 --> 00:01:00,383
Wei always tells me

29
00:01:00,383 --> 00:01:01,904
you make who he is now.

30
00:01:02,143 --> 00:01:02,743
Look.

31
00:01:03,463 --> 00:01:04,544
And thank you.

32
00:01:04,544 --> 00:01:05,824
Last time, if you hadn't put

33
00:01:05,824 --> 00:01:06,944
in a word with the police,

34
00:01:06,944 --> 00:01:08,143
my brother's fight incident...

35
00:01:09,023 --> 00:01:10,104
Thank you once again.

36
00:01:10,904 --> 00:01:11,943
No need to mention it.

37
00:01:11,943 --> 00:01:12,703
Let's drop this.

38
00:01:12,703 --> 00:01:13,783
Come on.

39
00:01:18,544 --> 00:01:19,423
Feng,

40
00:01:19,904 --> 00:01:21,904
when I walked into this bar,

41
00:01:21,904 --> 00:01:23,863
I noticed every seat was taken.

42
00:01:23,863 --> 00:01:25,664
Now every place
in this industry is packed.

43
00:01:25,664 --> 00:01:26,503
How about

44
00:01:27,063 --> 00:01:29,143
we start a nightclub or something?

45
00:01:30,544 --> 00:01:31,824
Great idea.

46
00:01:31,824 --> 00:01:32,984
Open our own place?

47
00:01:34,744 --> 00:01:35,423
Drink.

48
00:01:35,624 --> 00:01:36,303
Lu.

49
00:01:36,303 --> 00:01:36,803
Lu.

50
00:01:36,824 --> 00:01:37,583
Wake up.

51
00:01:38,604 --> 00:01:39,104
Drink.

52
00:01:39,104 --> 00:01:40,143
Listen up, everyone.

53
00:01:40,143 --> 00:01:41,384
- Drink? Drink what?
- Drink!

54
00:01:42,703 --> 00:01:44,423
I think Jiasheng's idea is doable.

55
00:01:44,943 --> 00:01:45,863
Look.

56
00:01:46,264 --> 00:01:48,343
Our resources and connections,

57
00:01:49,024 --> 00:01:51,824
plus you two's social skills

58
00:01:51,824 --> 00:01:52,904
and capabilities,

59
00:01:53,184 --> 00:01:55,343
and the current market conditions

60
00:01:55,343 --> 00:01:57,063
are perfect timing, location, and unity.

61
00:01:57,063 --> 00:01:57,744
Right?

62
00:01:57,744 --> 00:01:58,744
Exactly.

63
00:01:59,223 --> 00:02:01,223
Absolutely right.

64
00:02:01,264 --> 00:02:03,464
If we do it, let's make it high-end.

65
00:02:03,503 --> 00:02:04,264
Average people

66
00:02:04,624 --> 00:02:06,143
aren't even qualified to enter.

67
00:02:06,143 --> 00:02:06,643
Cheers.

68
00:02:06,664 --> 00:02:07,184
Come on.

69
00:02:07,184 --> 00:02:07,783
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

70
00:02:07,783 --> 00:02:08,943
It's settled then.

71
00:02:09,104 --> 00:02:10,423
We'll do this together.

72
00:02:10,624 --> 00:02:11,223
Bottoms up.

73
00:02:11,303 --> 00:02:12,303
- Bottoms up!
- Bottoms up!

74
00:02:13,717 --> 00:02:16,480
=The Glory Fades=

75
00:02:17,184 --> 00:02:19,456
=Episode 18=
(The Final Madness)

76
00:02:19,544 --> 00:02:20,264
Save me.

77
00:02:20,264 --> 00:02:21,463
Help!

78
00:02:21,463 --> 00:02:22,264
Contact Chief Zheng.

79
00:02:22,384 --> 00:02:23,264
Track the location.

80
00:02:23,623 --> 00:02:25,224
It's useless.

81
00:02:25,784 --> 00:02:28,423
No one can save you,

82
00:02:28,824 --> 00:02:29,583
including

83
00:02:29,703 --> 00:02:31,064
Tu Jiasheng.

84
00:02:32,623 --> 00:02:33,743
No one

85
00:02:34,344 --> 00:02:35,583
can escape

86
00:02:36,143 --> 00:02:38,064
my grasp alive.

87
00:02:41,423 --> 00:02:42,264
Mr. Zhao, Mr. Tu,

88
00:02:42,264 --> 00:02:42,984
you're here.

89
00:02:42,984 --> 00:02:44,064
In critical condition,

90
00:02:44,064 --> 00:02:44,863
no small talk.

91
00:02:44,863 --> 00:02:46,064
Brief us on the situation.

92
00:02:46,064 --> 00:02:47,743
We've preliminarily identified the area.

93
00:02:47,743 --> 00:02:48,504
But

94
00:02:48,928 --> 00:02:49,664
it's in Nanmanluo.

95
00:02:49,664 --> 00:02:50,984
Haven't pinpointed the location.

96
00:02:50,984 --> 00:02:51,944
That'll take some time.

97
00:02:51,944 --> 00:02:53,544
Because we're seriously short-staffed.

98
00:02:53,544 --> 00:02:54,824
Saturation rescue, got it?

99
00:02:54,824 --> 00:02:55,743
Deploy your men.

100
00:02:55,743 --> 00:02:56,824
They need travel time.

101
00:02:58,664 --> 00:02:59,824
You just said

102
00:03:00,264 --> 00:03:01,183
Nanmanluo District?

103
00:03:01,183 --> 00:03:02,384
Yeah, Nanmanluo District.

104
00:03:03,984 --> 00:03:04,504
Lu,

105
00:03:04,824 --> 00:03:06,064
I'll contact the military.

106
00:03:06,064 --> 00:03:07,264
Do what you must.

107
00:03:07,324 --> 00:03:07,824
Okay.

108
00:03:07,824 --> 00:03:08,743
I'll bring the SWAT.

109
00:03:10,463 --> 00:03:11,583
You have five minutes.

110
00:03:11,583 --> 00:03:12,623
I need the exact location.

111
00:03:12,944 --> 00:03:13,444
Yes.

112
00:03:24,143 --> 00:03:25,023
Take care, Mr. Tu.

113
00:03:32,544 --> 00:03:33,824
Everyone, parking lot, now!

114
00:03:33,824 --> 00:03:34,368
Ready to go.

115
00:03:34,368 --> 00:03:35,264
Hurry up.

116
00:03:53,536 --> 00:03:56,512
(Police Bureau, Changqingtai City)

117
00:04:12,384 --> 00:04:13,984
I can't wait any longer.

118
00:04:14,824 --> 00:04:16,703
Let's start with an appetizer.

119
00:04:17,224 --> 00:04:18,664
Come on, baby.

120
00:04:19,583 --> 00:04:21,064
This is only the first one.

121
00:04:21,824 --> 00:04:23,024
The mission is tough.

122
00:04:24,464 --> 00:04:25,904
There are nine more.

123
00:04:28,024 --> 00:04:29,664
Just kill me.

124
00:04:30,383 --> 00:04:32,183
Dying is easy.

125
00:04:32,904 --> 00:04:34,464
But you can't die now.

126
00:04:35,104 --> 00:04:37,464
Because if you die, these nails

127
00:04:37,823 --> 00:04:39,183
won't stay fresh anymore.

128
00:04:39,623 --> 00:04:40,784
You lunatic!

129
00:04:41,104 --> 00:04:42,063
Lunatic!

130
00:04:42,063 --> 00:04:43,464
(1999)

131
00:04:43,464 --> 00:04:44,863
Qin Wei, are you insane?

132
00:04:45,423 --> 00:04:46,704
What are you doing?

133
00:05:03,904 --> 00:05:05,464
I want your life.

134
00:05:08,584 --> 00:05:10,464
Even if I can't take your life,

135
00:05:13,784 --> 00:05:15,183
I'll take your face.

136
00:05:18,664 --> 00:05:20,664
Jiasheng won't spare you.

137
00:05:21,383 --> 00:05:22,183
Yes.

138
00:05:22,664 --> 00:05:24,464
He won't spare me.

139
00:05:24,623 --> 00:05:26,823
But Feng won't spare him either.

140
00:05:35,423 --> 00:05:36,464
Hello, Lu.

141
00:05:36,904 --> 00:05:38,664
Found Feng's entry record?

142
00:05:39,224 --> 00:05:40,863
Entry record? Not yet.

143
00:05:41,063 --> 00:05:42,784
Why are you suddenly asking about this?

144
00:05:44,024 --> 00:05:45,303
You don't think it's...

145
00:05:48,984 --> 00:05:49,664
Faster.

146
00:05:49,943 --> 00:05:50,503
Okay.

147
00:06:10,224 --> 00:06:11,623
Tu Jiasheng,

148
00:06:14,224 --> 00:06:15,863
you're ruthless.

149
00:06:21,263 --> 00:06:23,383
You've destroyed me.

150
00:06:31,584 --> 00:06:33,584
None of us will get away unscathed.

151
00:06:35,823 --> 00:06:37,904
None will get away unscathed.

152
00:06:41,503 --> 00:06:42,823
None will get away unscathed.

153
00:06:43,664 --> 00:06:45,503
None will get away unscathed.

154
00:06:48,503 --> 00:06:50,263
You made me into this monster.

155
00:06:50,584 --> 00:06:52,984
But I don't even know you.

156
00:06:54,584 --> 00:06:55,863
You don't know me,

157
00:06:57,104 --> 00:06:58,823
but Tu Jiasheng knows me.

158
00:06:59,904 --> 00:07:01,104
Zhao Lu knows me.

159
00:07:01,303 --> 00:07:02,623
Bai Manni knows me.

160
00:07:02,823 --> 00:07:04,144
And the dead An Ruoxi

161
00:07:04,144 --> 00:07:05,423
knew me.

162
00:07:13,504 --> 00:07:19,264
(Ambulance)

163
00:07:20,896 --> 00:07:22,208
(Ambulance)

164
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,712
(Police)

165
00:07:27,263 --> 00:07:28,863
Mr. Tu, I just spoke with Mr. Zhao.

166
00:07:28,863 --> 00:07:29,503
Break the door.

167
00:07:29,503 --> 00:07:30,503
Second option, to appeal

168
00:07:30,503 --> 00:07:31,224
to reason.

169
00:07:31,224 --> 00:07:32,503
Third option, shoot on sight.

170
00:07:32,503 --> 00:07:33,503
Which one works best?

171
00:07:33,503 --> 00:07:34,464
We can adjust any plan.

172
00:07:34,464 --> 00:07:35,423
Mr. Tu, I think

173
00:07:35,423 --> 00:07:36,784
hostage safety comes first.

174
00:07:36,784 --> 00:07:37,904
Blow the door open.

175
00:07:42,383 --> 00:07:43,183
You're all the same.

176
00:07:43,544 --> 00:07:44,664
You all deserve to die.

177
00:07:49,104 --> 00:07:50,863
An Ruoxi is dead now.

178
00:07:51,063 --> 00:07:51,743
Soon,

179
00:07:51,823 --> 00:07:53,503
you'll join her.

180
00:07:54,664 --> 00:07:58,224
So you killed An Ruoxi?

181
00:07:58,623 --> 00:07:59,904
Let me tell you,

182
00:07:59,904 --> 00:08:01,984
my biggest regret

183
00:08:02,183 --> 00:08:03,063
is failing

184
00:08:03,063 --> 00:08:05,024
to kill An Ruoxi myself.

185
00:08:06,224 --> 00:08:07,063
So

186
00:08:07,664 --> 00:08:09,104
who killed An Ruoxi?

187
00:08:12,104 --> 00:08:13,503
Tu Jiasheng...

188
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,826
You!

189
00:09:10,143 --> 00:09:11,104
Let me go!

190
00:09:11,304 --> 00:09:12,344
Let me go!

191
00:09:12,503 --> 00:09:13,503
Stay back!

192
00:09:14,143 --> 00:09:15,224
Let me go!

193
00:09:15,283 --> 00:09:16,584
- Yunian,
- Stay away!

194
00:09:16,743 --> 00:09:17,543
- it's me.
- Stay away!

195
00:09:23,903 --> 00:09:25,743
What took you so long?

196
00:09:27,263 --> 00:09:29,424
I was about to die, you know?

197
00:09:35,104 --> 00:09:35,903
It's okay.

198
00:09:38,503 --> 00:09:39,543
Any other injuries?

199
00:10:32,663 --> 00:10:33,464
Mr. Tu.

200
00:10:44,730 --> 00:10:45,291
Mr. Tu,

201
00:10:45,691 --> 00:10:47,490
we've conducted
a comprehensive examination.

202
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:49,490
Apart from a fingernail pulled out,

203
00:10:50,051 --> 00:10:50,971
no other injuries.

204
00:10:51,370 --> 00:10:52,451
All vital signs

205
00:10:52,530 --> 00:10:53,370
are in normal ranges.

206
00:10:53,850 --> 00:10:55,971
We've administered
the best painkillers available.

207
00:10:56,850 --> 00:10:58,850
The most crucial thing now
is adequate rest

208
00:10:58,850 --> 00:11:00,250
to aid wound recovery.

209
00:11:00,370 --> 00:11:01,571
In that case,

210
00:11:01,571 --> 00:11:02,490
you may go back.

211
00:11:03,370 --> 00:11:04,931
You've worked hard for so long.

212
00:11:05,691 --> 00:11:06,490
Wang.

213
00:11:16,370 --> 00:11:18,730
If any of your men talk out of turn,

214
00:11:19,051 --> 00:11:20,250
it won't just be

215
00:11:20,411 --> 00:11:22,331
about refunds.

216
00:11:24,451 --> 00:11:25,971
It might cost your life.

217
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:37,770
Mr. Tu,

218
00:11:39,051 --> 00:11:41,610
we'll take him back shortly.

219
00:11:41,770 --> 00:11:43,291
Kidnapping plus intentional assault,

220
00:11:43,291 --> 00:11:44,691
ten years max is a given.

221
00:11:47,211 --> 00:11:48,010
Ten years?

222
00:11:54,971 --> 00:11:55,691
Zheng,

223
00:11:56,211 --> 00:11:57,331
leave him with me.

224
00:11:58,211 --> 00:11:59,010
You all go.

225
00:12:00,051 --> 00:12:00,730
Mr. Tu,

226
00:12:01,250 --> 00:12:02,890
this might dirty your hands.

227
00:12:07,370 --> 00:12:08,730
Tomorrow, the news will report

228
00:12:08,931 --> 00:12:12,530
that an explosion occurred here
where someone produced flammable gas.

229
00:12:13,850 --> 00:12:14,370
Well,

230
00:12:14,451 --> 00:12:15,530
what do you need me to do?

231
00:12:17,890 --> 00:12:19,171
Tie him up and head back.

232
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:20,691
Next,

233
00:12:20,890 --> 00:12:21,931
Lu will contact you.

234
00:12:22,171 --> 00:12:23,051
For the aftermath,

235
00:12:25,091 --> 00:12:25,890
old rules apply.

236
00:12:28,211 --> 00:12:28,730
Mr. Tu,

237
00:12:28,971 --> 00:12:30,370
we're not strangers.

238
00:12:30,370 --> 00:12:31,571
That's not what I meant.

239
00:12:35,291 --> 00:12:37,291
Your men need to make a living.

240
00:12:37,971 --> 00:12:38,850
Well,

241
00:12:38,850 --> 00:12:39,971
thanks, Mr. Tu.

242
00:12:40,850 --> 00:12:41,650
Back to it, then.

243
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:07,211
It's my fault.

244
00:13:09,691 --> 00:13:10,730
Not your concern.

245
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:12,811
You don't have to do this.

246
00:13:12,971 --> 00:13:13,770
No,

247
00:13:15,130 --> 00:13:16,331
it is my concern.

248
00:13:18,451 --> 00:13:19,890
I shouldn't have let you go alone.

249
00:13:23,171 --> 00:13:24,291
I've walked

250
00:13:25,370 --> 00:13:27,130
this road countless times.

251
00:13:27,811 --> 00:13:28,610
So

252
00:13:29,770 --> 00:13:30,770
it was me

253
00:13:32,530 --> 00:13:34,130
who made you their target.

254
00:13:37,811 --> 00:13:38,850
Mr. Tu,

255
00:13:38,850 --> 00:13:40,331
you've certainly made many enemies.

256
00:13:41,451 --> 00:13:42,250
No wonder.

257
00:13:42,730 --> 00:13:43,530
No wonder what?

258
00:13:44,610 --> 00:13:45,650
No wonder

259
00:13:47,211 --> 00:13:49,091
Ruoxi died such a horrible death.

260
00:14:00,571 --> 00:14:01,770
That's why I kept stopping you

261
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:03,171
from entering Deep In The Bustle

262
00:14:03,571 --> 00:14:04,650
and getting involved.

263
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:06,171
Yes,

264
00:14:06,971 --> 00:14:07,971
I shouldn't have come.

265
00:14:08,650 --> 00:14:11,051
I never should have gotten entangled
with you in any way.

266
00:14:12,370 --> 00:14:13,890
But I want the truth.

267
00:14:14,130 --> 00:14:15,811
I want to find the real killer,

268
00:14:15,811 --> 00:14:17,370
and put them behind bars.

269
00:14:18,331 --> 00:14:19,291
Tu Jiasheng,

270
00:14:19,850 --> 00:14:20,610
Mr. Tu,

271
00:14:21,971 --> 00:14:23,091
don't you want that?

272
00:14:29,171 --> 00:14:30,291
Starting today,

273
00:14:30,730 --> 00:14:32,451
you're moving into Room 999.

274
00:14:35,850 --> 00:14:36,610
No need.

275
00:14:38,411 --> 00:14:39,530
Just take me home.

276
00:14:39,650 --> 00:14:41,291
You need to stay by my side.

277
00:14:41,691 --> 00:14:43,091
I'm saying this one last time.

278
00:14:43,691 --> 00:14:45,171
Take me home.

279
00:14:45,850 --> 00:14:47,370
Don't you want to avenge Ruoxi?

280
00:15:05,331 --> 00:15:06,010
Mr. Tu,

281
00:15:06,331 --> 00:15:07,331
everything's arranged.

282
00:15:07,331 --> 00:15:08,571
The demolition team is set.

283
00:15:09,530 --> 00:15:10,331
Head back first.

284
00:15:10,331 --> 00:15:11,650
Leave him to me.

285
00:15:14,571 --> 00:15:16,051
Send her back to Room 999 safely.

286
00:15:17,610 --> 00:15:18,130
Okay.

287
00:16:02,051 --> 00:16:03,171
What happened to you?

288
00:16:04,490 --> 00:16:05,770
Neither human nor ghost,

289
00:16:06,571 --> 00:16:07,890
neither man nor woman.

290
00:16:13,730 --> 00:16:14,530
Tu Jiasheng,

291
00:16:15,650 --> 00:16:16,490
all this

292
00:16:17,811 --> 00:16:19,490
is your doing, isn't it?

293
00:16:20,770 --> 00:16:21,811
Me?

294
00:16:23,650 --> 00:16:25,051
Isn't it?

295
00:16:27,091 --> 00:16:28,291
Who

296
00:16:30,051 --> 00:16:31,770
made me betray Feng?

297
00:16:34,130 --> 00:16:35,130
Who

298
00:16:37,171 --> 00:16:38,331
has left me

299
00:16:38,730 --> 00:16:39,571
abandoned,

300
00:16:39,571 --> 00:16:40,490
living without dignity,

301
00:16:40,490 --> 00:16:41,811
existing without purpose?

302
00:16:44,171 --> 00:16:45,051
Who made me

303
00:16:46,091 --> 00:16:46,971
abandon my conscience

304
00:16:46,971 --> 00:16:49,010
and commit those vile, atrocious deeds?

305
00:16:51,490 --> 00:16:52,490
Wasn't it you?

306
00:17:07,610 --> 00:17:08,411
Tu Jiasheng,

307
00:17:10,611 --> 00:17:12,090
I just want to ask you one question.

308
00:17:15,411 --> 00:17:16,570
Before I die,

309
00:17:20,971 --> 00:17:22,691
can you answer me truthfully?

310
00:17:23,891 --> 00:17:24,570
Will you?

311
00:17:24,570 --> 00:17:25,371
Go ahead.

312
00:17:28,651 --> 00:17:29,730
Back then,

313
00:17:30,131 --> 00:17:31,211
during that drinking party,

314
00:17:34,891 --> 00:17:35,851
at that very night,

315
00:17:38,651 --> 00:17:40,451
did you mean it when you

316
00:17:43,570 --> 00:17:45,971
said those things to me?

317
00:17:53,792 --> 00:17:57,466
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

318
00:17:57,765 --> 00:18:00,956
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

319
00:18:02,788 --> 00:18:06,409
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

320
00:18:06,958 --> 00:18:09,888
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

321
00:18:11,228 --> 00:18:14,958
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

322
00:18:15,182 --> 00:18:18,848
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

323
00:18:20,078 --> 00:18:23,765
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

324
00:18:24,403 --> 00:18:29,568
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

325
00:18:30,222 --> 00:18:34,356
♪I feel guilty♪

326
00:18:34,926 --> 00:18:38,670
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

327
00:18:39,534 --> 00:18:42,977
♪Even in tears♪

328
00:18:43,726 --> 00:18:47,640
♪It doesn't matter♪

329
00:18:47,822 --> 00:18:51,645
♪We embrace in dreams♪

330
00:18:52,494 --> 00:18:55,932
♪I let down all my defenses♪

331
00:18:57,166 --> 00:19:00,529
♪Though the story has its end♪

332
00:19:01,294 --> 00:19:08,704
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
